How to accept DAI / USDC / Any other ERC20 Token from Metamask to your smart contract
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Original code taken from Gregory's Dapp University:
https://www.dappuniversity.com/videos/CgXQC4dbGUE
https://github.com/dappuniversity/defi_tutorial

Deploy TokenFarm contract on kovan:
truffle migrate --network kovan --reset -f 2 

UI:
npm start run
